    "ICO is an alternative way of financing projects or startups by creating and issuing tokens on a blockchain and selling them to raise funds.",
    "IEOs can be seen as an ICO supervised by cryptocurrency exchange platforms: the project goes through due diligence before commencing the sale, which gives investors more assurance about the validity and success of the project.",
